      <title>Eldridge 旗下投资公司 Panagram 首席执行官辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ceo-of-eldridge-owned-investment-firm-panagram-resigns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周二上午提交的文件显示，Panagram Structured Asset Management 首席执行官 John E. Kim 已向公司辞职，立即生效。]]></description>
